extends layout

block content
	div(class="ek-page")#top
		include parts/resume/topbar
		h1(class="animBor")
			span(class="first-name")= "Robin "
			span(class="last-name") Mollah
		br
		include sections/quote
		div(id="next-page-holder")
			div(id="next-page") &#11015;
		div
			span
	include parts/resume/search-skill.pug
	include parts/resume/project-showcase.pug
	include parts/resume/experiences.pug
	p(id="cv_content").
		I started coding from an early age because I believe through technology I can make a huge national and global impact.
		I would love to be a contributor in creating a history of technology-based society.
		Being part of something that makes an upgrade in any part of this world is the most desired dream of my life.
	br
	script(type="text/javascript" src="/javascripts/skill-viewer.js")
	script.
		document.getElementById("next-page").addEventListener("click", function(){
			document.getElementById("skill-search").scrollIntoView({behavior: "smooth", inline: "nearest"});
		});
